high_descs: Go forward to the stove top, at the oven turn right, go forward, turn right at the end of the kitchen island and face the kitchen island counter.
Take the small knife from the counter.
Turn right, go forward to the stove top, turn right to face the counter to the right of the stove top.
Cut the lettuce next to the toaster into slices.
Turn around, go forward, turn right at the fridge, go to the fridge.
Put the knife on the lowest shelf in the center and near the edge in the fridge.
Turn right, go forward to the counter to the right of the stove top.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn around, go straight and to the left to the counter to the right of the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink. Take the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around, go forward, make a left to the fridge, go to the fridge.
Put the lettuce on the lowest shelf in the fridge to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of lettuce in a fridge.

high_descs: Move forward around the counter and face the counter with the knife on it on your right.
Pick up the knife on the counter in front of you.
Turn right then face the lettuce on the counter to your right.
Slice the lettuce on the left of the toaster on the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge to your right.
Open the fridge, place the knife inside and close the fridge.
Turn right and head towards the counter with the toaster.
Take a lettuce slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the sink in front of you.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and take it out.
Turn around and face the fridge to your left.
Place the lettuce slice in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean lettuce slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the island near the pan.
Pick up the knife that is near the pan.
Turn to the right, move to the counter in front of the toaster.
Slice the lettuce on the counter that is nearest the toaster.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife into the refrigerator.
Turn to the right, move to the counter in front of the toaster.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn left, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Place the slice of lettuce into the sink, rinse it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the slice of lettuce into the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed slice of lettuce into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Walk to the stove the turn right and face the island counter.
Pick up the knife near the pan on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Slice the lettuce on the back of counter.
Turn left and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the knife inside the refrigerator and close the door.
Turn around to the counter behind you then turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink and turn on the water to rinse the lettuce then remove the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator on your left.
Put the lettuce in the refrigerator and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice the lettuce, rinse the lettuce in the sink, put the lettuce in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Keeping the fridge and counters to your left, walk around the island to the opposite corner.  Face the kitchen island, keeping the wall on your left and the kitchen counter behind you.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen island that is just behind the metal skillet.
Turn to the right and walk towards the stove top, stopping just before reaching it.  Face the counter with the toaster on it.
Slice half of the green vegetable to the left of the toaster, just right of the stove top.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, place the knife on the bottom shelf in front of the tomato, and shut the door.
Turn right and walk back to the counter in between the toaster and stove top.
Pick up one slice of green vegetable that is next to the toaster.
Turn left and walk past the fridge to the sink.
Put the slice of green vegetable into the sink, fill the sink with water then drain it.  Take out the slice of green vegetable.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the slice of green vegetable on the bottom shelf, just to the right of the knife. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and rinsed slice of green vegetable into the fridge.

high_descs: Walk past the refrigerator and make a right at the stove, then turn to your right so that you are between the kitchen island and the kitchen counter.
Pick up the knife in front of the fry pan, on the kitchen island.
Turn to your right and walk towards the toaster on the counter to your right.
Cut the head of lettuce on the counter in the far back into slices.
Go to the refrigerator, to your left while holding the knife.
Place the knife on the shelf just above the drawers, in the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and walk back to the counter with the sliced lettuce on it.
Pick up a slice of the lettuce previously cut that is on the back of the counter.
Turn around and walk past the kitchen island to the sink.
Place the slice of lettuce into the sink, turn the water on, rinse the lettuce, turn the water off and remove the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the refrigerator to your left.
Place the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator, on the shelf just above the drawers, to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.
